{"tid":1434964,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢裝備係咪應該加入哨子？","createTime":"2019-08-09T02:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:09:01.000Z","uid":157365,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5098825406b1ffdc468035564976b010ab2d6b80","tid":1434964,"uid":157365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:16:58.000Z","msg":"最近發夢，覺得現場所有嘅訊息都係用嗌嚟傳遞，一方面嗌嗰條友好辛苦，好多時發完一晚夢返去把聲沙晒，二嚟訊息好混亂，傳播速度唔夠快。<br />\n<br />\n如果用哨子，共識一啲暗號<br />\n例如<br />\n「嗶。嗶。嗶。嗶」=向前<br />\n「嗶～～～～～～」=引前方危險向後走<br />\n<br />\n咁樣大家嘅組織會好啲，唔會成盤散沙咁"},{"pid":"f13eb824d2a3960642b461bf4ad64ba2e8f6106a","tid":1434964,"uid":157365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24cdd8d3affb1fb8f7603f000db58e3106615d4b","tid":1434964,"uid":157365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d49e32d7b0cee8889ca304c4e10743bd2d3db083","tid":1434964,"uid":157365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d48d8a2ddb2d94f16026bb100ca20343f74a5bf","tid":1434964,"uid":115728,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"如果有幾個人有哨子，就只會不停向前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87a123f3886b00181077e74aec47a9547c24a46","tid":1434964,"uid":261995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7740ce0bc4a42e1c5b92ba257940e29a2c3a9145","tid":1434964,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"成日都上唔到網"},{"pid":"d48dc49122b902604350ae866190195598abc7cc","tid":1434964,"uid":244889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"變咗大台"},{"pid":"7449251c341a4bb7ed378fc8a8dc7caf4db943d0","tid":1434964,"uid":157365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor